Description_lang: At 100 energy, Sikran swings his polearm in a deadly arc, inflicting $458277s1 Shadow damage to all enemies. This damage is decreased based on distance. All remaining Cosmic Simulacrum are destroyed by this effect, and damage from $@spellname459273 is increased by $464442s1% for each Simulacrum destroyed for $464442d.Additionally, players within $458277A2 yards are knocked back and have their damage taken increased by $458277s2% for $458277d.
